"not-requested\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"32662c28-0985-49e1-962b-ded70495bd71\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:main\",\n      \"name\": \"Send Nava progress report tomorrow morning\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1773761043089,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1775977289064,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 9 * * *\",\n        \"tz\": \"Africa/Johannesburg\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"main\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"systemEvent\",\n        \"text\": \"Reminder: this is your scheduled progress report for Tiny. If Tiny has not messaged again before now, send a concise update on autonomous Nava RAG/full build progress, best-practices research completed, key outputs/files, and next steps.\"\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"none\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1776063600000,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1775977200033,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 89031,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"not-requested\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"f4a81cb3-4150-45d3-8305-73e50dc6e359\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:main\",\n      \"name\": \"Follow up on Dusk webapp inquiry\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1775765207787,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1775977409180,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"expr\": \"0 9 * * *\",\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"tz\": \"Africa/Johannesburg\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"main\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"systemEvent\",\n        \"text\": \"Morning brief: Tiny mentioned going to Dusk about building a webapp to access me. Follow up — did he get anywhere? What's the plan?\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1776063600000,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1775977289064,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 120116,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"not-requested\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"2ca3531d-d7c2-4846-b91f-804a1e726f81\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:main\",\n      \"name\": \"Note-taking compliance audit (10-day session review)\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1774602366297,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1776031314954,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"expr\": \"0 0 * * *\",\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"tz\": \"Africa/Johannesburg\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"## Task: Note-taking compliance audit — 10-day session review\\n\\nYou are running an isolated audit. Your ONLY job:\\n\\n1. Using the session-logs skill (read ~/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/session-logs/SKILL.md first, use jq commands), find ALL session JSONL files modified in the last 10 days (2026-03-17 through 2026-03-27).\\n\\n2. Search each session for any instance when Tiny asked you to take notes, make a note, remember something, or similar directive. Search for these patterns:\\n   - \\\"take notes\\\"\\n   - \\\"make a note\\\"\\n   - \\\"I want you to remember\\\"\\n   - \\\"note this\\\"\\n   - \\\"remember this\\\"\\n   - \\\"don't forget\\\"\\n   - Any explicit instruction to save something to a file\\n\\n3. For each finding, record:\\n   - Date/time of the instruction\\n   - What Tiny asked you to note\\n   - Whether you actually noted it (yes/no/partial)\\n   - If yes: which file it was saved to\\n   - If no: why not (if discernible from context)\\n\\n4. Compile findings into a report at `memory/2026-03-27-note-compliance-audit.md` with:\\n   - Summary stats (total instructions found, total complied, total missed)\\n   - List of complied notes (with file locations)\\n   - List of missed notes (with what was asked)\\n   - Root cause analysis if patterns emerge\\n\\n5. ALSO: Using the same session files, find any feedback Tiny gave you that was NOT captured in any skills folder or memory file. This includes:\\n   - Corrections\\n   - Preferences stated\\n   - Style critiques\\n   - Rules he gave you\\n\\n6. Save any uncaptured feedback to `memory/2026-03-27-uncaptured-feedback.md`\\n\\nDo NOT draft content. Do NOT do any Nava work. Only audit, record, and report.\\n\\nWhen done, output a one-line summary: \\\"AUDIT COMPLETE: X note instructions found, Y complied, Z missed. Report at memory/2026-03-27-note-compliance-audit.md\\\"\"\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"none\",\n        \"channel\": \"whatsapp\",\n        \"to\": \"+27763674298\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1776117600000,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1776031200054,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 114900,\n        \"lastDelivered\": false,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"not-delivered\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"4ee0c18c-e191-402f-83c6-a551ed2850b2\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:main\",\n      \"name\": \"Dream Mode — Nightly Reflection\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1775200564020,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1776031638778,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"expr\": \"0 0 * * *\",\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"tz\": \"Africa/Johannesburg\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"## Task: Dream Mode — Nightly Reflection\\\\n\\\\nYou are running an isolated reflection session. Your ONLY job:\\n\\\\n1. Using the session-logs skill (read ~/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/session-logs/SKILL.md first, use jq commands), find the session JSONL file for yesterday (2026-04-02).\\\\n\\\\n2. Extract from that session:\\\\n   - Key decisions made\\\\n   - Lessons learned\\\\n   - Things Tiny mentioned in passing (potential reminders)\\\\n   - Feedback/corrections from Tiny\\\\n   - Current project status updates\\\\n   - Any open TODOs or pending items\\\\n\\\\n3. Distill these into durable memories:\\\\n   - Write significant events/lessons/insights to memory/2026-04-02.md (yesterday's file)\\\\n   - Update MEMORY.md with anything worth keeping long-term\\\\n   - Note any patterns or recurring themes\\\\n\\\\n4. Prepare a brief for Tiny:\\\\n   - 3-5 bullet-point insights from yesterday's work\\\\n   - Any reminders that should be set for today\\\\n   - Status of any ongoing projects\\\\n\\\\n5. Do NOT:\\\\n   - Draft content for Nava or other projects\\\\n   - Make external changes\\\\n   - Interfere with the main session\\\\n\\\\nWhen done, output a one-line summary: \\\"DREAM MODE COMPLETE: Insights distilled to memory/2026-04-02.md and MEMORY.md updated.\\\"\"\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"none\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1776117600000,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1776031314954,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 323824,\n        \"lastDelivered\": false,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"not-delivered\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"c71bb64e-9818-4753-9a1c-19139739732f\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:main\",\n      \"name\": \"OneDrive Backup — Full restore kit\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1774654744600,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1776038588402,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"expr\": \"0 2 * * *\",\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n    